"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/wifedom-review-orwell-a-portrait-of-her-marriage-fb31ab2c?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《妻子》评论：她婚姻的写照</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/wifedom-review-orwell-a-portrait-of-her-marriage-fb31ab2c"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-833555?width=700&amp;height=455" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">伦敦大学学院特别收藏</span></div></div></div><p>乔治·奥威尔的第一任妻子在他的文学生涯中扮演了一个被低估的角色，并且看到了他与他的公众形象并不总是相符的一面。<em>唐娜·里夫金德评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/wifedom-review-orwell-a-portrait-of-her-marriage-fb31ab2c?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
